lead_paragraph: The defending Olympic pole vault champion warmed up, then cooled down, then ran through the whole process again, as the driving rain pelted the field Friday at U.S. Olympic Trials.

headline.print_headline: Rain, Tears and Teens With Olympic Track Spots on the Line
